00466                             default:

00469                                    break;
00470                             }
00471                      break;
00472

00474                      statusText = QObject::tr("Processing canceled by user");
00475                      break;
00476

00478                      statusText = QObject::tr("Processing not possible");
00479                      statusIcon = QIcon(":/Icons/StateInvalid.svg");

00481

00483                      statusText = QObject::tr("Critical error occurred, application problem");
